OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA Bromley Council spokesperson said,
OL,8,F"All approaches for housing assistance
OL,9,Fin Bromley are carefully checked to
OL,10,Fensure that a housing duty is rightly
OL,11,Fowed.
OL,13,F"In this case, we have not received
OL,14,Fthe information to date to show that a
OL,15,Fhousing duty is owed by Bromley,
OL,16,Fhowever if further information comes
OL,17,Fto light, we will of course review
OL,18,Fthis, as we are committed to providing
OL,19,Fhousing in line with our statutory
OL,20,Fduties."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU|D@HO]
