CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Waltham Forest
OL,8,FCouncil said: "The family came to the
OL,9,Fattention of Waltham Forest Children's
OL,10,FServices last December. As soon as we
OL,11,Festablished the significance of their
OL,12,Fsituation, and with the knowledge that
OL,13,Fthey had previously presented as
OL,14,Fhomeless in another part of the
OL,15,Fcapital, our Housing team quickly
OL,16,Fstepped in to provide emergency
OL,17,Faccommodation.
OL,26,@pD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
