OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Locally we have seen homelessness
OL,8,Fdemand rise by 80 percent in just two
OL,9,Fyears. Research suggests boroughs
OL,10,Facross London are grappling with a
OL,11,Fshortfall of #1billion this financial
OL,12,Fyear alone, much of it going on
OL,13,Fproviding temporary accommodation."
OL,15,FOn Thursday, the government will
OL,16,Fpublish the annual rough sleeping
OL,17,Fstatistics for England, which are
OL,18,Fwidely expected to increase. Last year
OL,19,Fthe number of people sleeping rough
OL,20,Fincreased by 20% to 4,667, just below
OL,21,Fthe peak in 2017.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FGovernment data on how many children
OL,8,Fare living in temporary accommodation
OL,9,Fwill also be published on Thursday.
OL,10,FThe current number - 172, 420 - is the
OL,11,Fhighest on record.
OL,13,FYet ITV News has spoken to families
OL,14,Fbeing denied even temporary
OL,15,Faccommodation when they become
OL,16,Fhomeless.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
