OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIn Birmingham, Mechelle and her three
OL,8,Fchildren were forced to sleep in their
OL,9,Fcar last year after Birmingham City
OL,10,FCouncil refused to provide
OL,11,Faccommodation.
OL,13,FMechelle and her young children were
OL,14,Fforced to sleep in their car
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe family are from Birmingham but had
OL,8,Fbeen living and renting in Cornwall.
OL,9,FHer three-year old son, who has a
OL,10,Flearning disability and epilepsy, was
OL,11,Fhaving more seizures, so she decided
OL,12,Fto move back to Birmingham to be
OL,13,Fcloser to family and a dedicated
OL,14,Fchildren's hospital.
OL,16,F"I thought in my own head that I could
OL,17,Fafford private rent and work like I've
OL,18,Falways done and paid my way," said
OL,19,FMechelle.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"I was actually on the street in the
OL,8,Fcar, there's no toilet, the kids
OL,9,Fcrying, my boy's having seizures.
OL,11,F"It was pretty damn scary, really, to
OL,12,Fbe honest. I was just petrified...you
OL,13,Fthink: Are we going to survive this?
OL,14,FWhat's going to happen? I honestly
OL,15,Fthought I was going to lose my kids to
OL,16,Fcare.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"I'm ashamed of the situation I put us
OL,8,Fin and the guilt that I carry that
OL,9,FI've had to put my kids through. My
OL,10,Fkids have got disabilities and they're
OL,11,Fnot entitled to the help and the
OL,12,Fsupport that they need. What else do
OL,13,Fyou do?"
OL,15,FITV News has approached Birmingham
OL,16,FCity Council for comment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]
