OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772016033
OL,3,CCouncils leave children as young as
OL,4,Cfour sleeping on the streets, ITV News
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHomelessness minister, Alison
OL,8,FMcGovern, said: "No child should be
OL,9,Fsleeping on the streets, and the law
OL,10,Fis absolutely clear on that - each
OL,11,Fcase is a failure of the system.
OL,13,F"Where there's any confusion, the
OL,14,Fcouncil approached must provide
OL,15,Finterim housing immediately, with
OL,16,Fdisputes resolved afterwards. No
OL,17,Fchild's safety should hinge on
OL,18,Fadministrative delays."
OL,26,@pD@QOUuD@AOU
